[0.6.0] - 2017-12-03

Added
- The poped-up about button with program name, version, author,
  copyright and update date on the forum page.
- The obvious characters list for escaping in the escape form on the
  forum page.

Changed
- Make cursor as a hand without selection on forum buttons.

Fixed
- Regexp meta-characters bug in the escape characters list on the
  forum page.
- The program update date for every program version wasn't written
  correctly to sources.

[0.5.1] - 2017-12-01

Added

Changed
- Moved forum HTML body event to the JavaScript script.
- Moved forum forms action handlers to the JavaScript script.

Fixed
- Forum comment, describing implemented features in the JavaScript
  script.
- Incorrect variable name in the forum escaping url function.
- Forum forms block minimal height was too small, so the footer
  shifted for one appeared form.

[0.5.0] - 2017-11-30

Added
